Name: Mutant Ops
About the game: Survive endless waves of enemies alone or with friends. Customize your loadout, using the strongest armor and weapons you can find. Deal massive amounts of burst damage with a sniper, or steady consistent damage with an ar. Have an arsenal full of weapons, or gear up with tons of armor, just. . . dont die.
Developers: Jacob Navarro (programming),Andrew Isaias (Mutant SFX),Aaron Sovann (backend programming),ElevateAudio (Music)
